  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (NC-10 clean)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. All 13 credibility factors are assessed; seven are fully met and six are scoped-out with documented rationale. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed and all factor requirements are satisfied. Decision: Accepted based on complete structured evidence with no residual shortfalls.",
