      },
      "rationale": "The commercial CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2024R1) is used under a validated license with documented version control and a complete regression test suite. All critical hemolysis-relevant solver modules pass regression checks. SQA documentation is archived and traceable to the project data management system."
