      "rationale": "A three-level mesh refinement study was performed on all 5 operating points. Richardson extrapolation yielded a maximum GCI of 3.8% on the hemolysis index, satisfying the < 5% acceptance threshold. Mesh independence is confirmed for the primary QoI."
